        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR3a0002-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_023-5a.42" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-13T23:31:25.571+09:00">is in his artificiality.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_023-5a.43" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-13T23:31:25.571+09:00">Now, to be fond of profit and desire to acquire it</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_023-5a.44" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-13T23:31:25.571+09:00">is the natural disposition of man.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_023-5a.45" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-13T23:31:25.571+09:00">Suppose a man has brothers and wealth to divide;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_023-5a.46" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-13T23:31:25.571+09:00">if they simply followed their natural disposition,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_023-5a.47" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-13T23:31:25.571+09:00">being fond of profit and desiring to acquire it,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_023-5a.48" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-13T23:31:25.571+09:00">then the brothers would contradict and seize from each other.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_023-5a.49" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-13T23:31:25.571+09:00">But if they transformed it with the patterns of ritual and righteousness,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_023-5a.50" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-13T23:31:25.571+09:00">then they would yield to the people of the state.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_023-5a.51" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-13T23:31:25.571+09:00">Therefore, following natural disposition causes brothers to contend;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_023-5a.52" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-13T23:31:25.571+09:00">transforming it with ritual and righteousness causes them to yield to the people of the state.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_023-5a.53" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-13T23:31:25.571+09:00">In general, the reason why people desire to do good</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_023-5a.54" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-13T23:31:25.571+09:00">is because their nature is evil.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_023-5a.55" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-13T23:31:25.571+09:00">Now, the meager desire abundance,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_023-5a.56" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-13T23:31:25.571+09:00">the ugly desire beauty,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_023-5a.57" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-13T23:31:25.571+09:00">the narrow desire breadth,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_023-5a.58" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-13T23:31:25.571+09:00">the poor desire wealth,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_023-5a.59" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-13T23:31:25.571+09:00">the lowly desire nobility;</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_023-5a.60" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-13T23:31:25.571+09:00">if one does not have something within himself,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_023-5a.61" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-13T23:31:25.571+09:00">he will surely seek it from without.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0002_tls_023-5a.62" xml:lang="en" resp="#gemini-2.0-flash" modified="2025-05-13T23:31:25.571+09:00">Therefore, the rich do not desire wealth,</seg>
                </p>
